Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Universul are un început, dar nu are sfârșit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.61,0:00:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Infinit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stelele, de asemenea, au un început,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.82,0:00:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,dar propria lor putere le distruge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cei ce posedă înțelepciune sunt adesea cei mai nerozi dintre toți.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Istoria ne-a dovedit acest lucru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ai putea spune că acesta este ultimul avertisment divin pentru cei ce se împotrivesc.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Să mergem.
